### Get Auth Token
# @name login
POST {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/auth/email/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{TEST_EMAIL}}",
  "password": "{{TEST_PASSWORD}}"
}

### Set token variable from login response
@token = {{login.token}}

### ===========================================
### PATCH COST CENTERS ENDPOINTS (UPDATE)
### ===========================================

### Update Cost Center (Update Remarks Only)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "remarks": "Updated remarks for cost center"
}

### Update Cost Center (Update Status)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "status": "Hold"
}

### Update Cost Center (Update Organizational Hierarchy)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division": "02",
  "department": "03",
  "section": "04",
  "sub_section": "05",
  "remarks": "Updated complete organizational hierarchy"
}

### Update Cost Center (Update Multiple Fields)
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "division": "03",
  "department": "04",
  "section": "05",
  "sub_section": "06",
  "remarks": "Updated multiple fields - hierarchy and status",
  "status": "Active"
}

### ===========================================
### STATUS UPDATE ENDPOINTS (SPECIFIC ROUTES)
### ===========================================

### Update Cost Center Status to Hold
PATCH {{BACKEND_DOMAIN}}/api/v1/cost-centers/1/hold
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
